ia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"news\", \"from\": 159, \"to\": 163}, {\"ngram\": \"every sports nut\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 198}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 202, \"to\": 213}, {\"ngram\": \"their 2024 Olympic Games coverage\", \"from\": 293, \"to\": 326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McAvaney was a mainstay on the Seven Network calling AFL and headlining the network's Olympics coverage for many years.\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 360, \"end\": 373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seven_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.9194856474735767e-14, \"text\": \"Seven Network\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seven_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seven_Network\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McAvaney\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 337}, {\"ngram\": \"a mainstay\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 352}, {\"ngram\": \"AFL\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 385}, {\"ngram\": \"the network's Olympics coverage\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 432}, {\"ngram\": \"many years\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He will step back into the spotlight to commentate the 2024 Paris Games for ABC radio.\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 526, \"end\": 529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9999999835522432, \"rank\": 8.856023098401221e-09, \"text\": \"ABC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the spotlight\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 486}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Games\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Having been involved in Olympic Games coverage since Los Angeles in 1984 and th