ia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9999988135278035, \"rank\": 1.055162849141646e-06, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 971, \"end\": 974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9999999835522432, \"rank\": 8.856023098401221e-09, \"text\": \"ABC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"the ultimate event\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 893}, {\"ngram\": \"this opportunity\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 963}, {\"ngram\": \"a great deal\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 993}, {\"ngram\": \"the presenter\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1015}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These games will be as exciting as any.\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These games\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have a 75-strong athletics team - our biggest we have ever sent overseas - and I am very optimistic they are ready to achieve great things.\\\"\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1224, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 75-strong athletics team\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1115}, {\"ngram\": \"great things\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ABC listeners will be able to hear live daily Olympics coverage from 6.30pm until close of competition across ABC Radio and DAB+.\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1355, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1226, \"end\": 1229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9999999835522432, \"rank\": 8.856023098401221e-0